description: People of San Francisco, come out to The Game Day Truck to simultaneously support your local teams as well as the dreams of Peter, Aaron, and Anthony; three cool dudes that share a passion for sports and delicious foods. With their combined talents, they’ve opened up The Game Day Truck, and by introducing a Cambodian influence to common game day cuisine, every dish they’re knocking out is a slam dunk. Their fresh slaw, papaya salad, house aioli, and Asian BBQ wing sauces are all made each morning fresh by hand. When you try this fantastic fare, The Game Day Truck will gain yet another fan. Touch down and go to town on this finger lickin’ fusion food!
name: The Game Day Truck
